    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just so frustrated because i've literally been staring at the ceiling for three hours already. the melatonin thing is fine but it's so weak. honestly i feel like i'm just overthinking the alcohol part. if i just take a tiny bit extra of the zolpidem instead of the wine, would that be a better way to make sure it actually works tonight? i just need to know if doubling up will help me sleep through the night since the single dose isn't doing much.",
